{"tid":2071503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧：關注香港立法會選舉 正在決定那些人要對遏制香港的自由負責","createTime":"2020-06-20T01:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T16:45:09.000Z","uid":125168,"like":363,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"a80f965a6e19f446e8943f60c3fc839dc3f73cf9","tid":2071503,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:37:18.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧稱香港9月選舉將可了解中共尊重香港自由意向<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧表示，如果中國將香港視為內地的其中一個城市，例如深圳和上海，美國將一視同仁，不會視香港為享有自治的城市，並放棄任何美國和香港之間訂立獨特協議。蓬佩奧在哥本哈根民主高峰會的視像會議表示，關注香港9月舉行的選舉，認為將令外界了解，中共在尊重香港自由方面的意向，又說華盛頓正展開程序，決定那些人要對遏制香港的自由負責。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-20 09:25:11<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/118604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F118604&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=b7913732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/118604</a>"},{"pid":"b7f58886c009dc4a615230f42cd61b63c68e5997","tid":2071503,"uid":125168,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:39:35.000Z","msg":"所有戰線都要打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c46ab4535c75ebc5b54e869ae7c214ddb95e02","tid":2071503,"uid":95138,"like":47,"dislike":4,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:39:36.000Z","msg":"泛民唔反對政府議案 = 政府唔DQ<br />\n自己吞左本身送俾美國粒子彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5474e94a1cfbb6f3c3c28bcdcf1997ce43237468","tid":2071503,"uid":95138,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b7f58886c009dc4a615230f42cd61b63c68e5997","tid":2071503,"uid":125168,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:39:35.000Z","msg":"所有戰線都要打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T01:40:28.000Z","msg":"點睇泛民吞子彈"},{"pid":"790690570176200aad764dad43f819a2e251bb62","tid":2071503,"uid":222238,"like":5,"dislike":58,"sco